title: American Popular Song - Six Decades Of Songwriters & Singers
description:
American Popular Song: Six Decades Of Songwriters & Singers (1984) - 
Companion Book to the Smithsonian Collection Of Recordings 5 CD Set.

This is the companion book to the 5 CD set of recordings and is essential for the full appreciation of the music that was chosen for the collection. It covers each of the recordings in detail including recording information, the composers/lyricists and the singers. Heavily illustrated. 151 pages.

Pages were individually scanned, cropped and compiled into a single PDF file.

(The recordings are available here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9845719)
